# Glass Compatibility Engine

## Purpose
Run applications from different platforms.

## Supported Formats
- .exe
- .msi
- .deb
- .rpm
- .AppImage
- .apk (future)
- .atp (Glass Native)

## Features
- Automatic App Detection
- Automatic Key Mapping
- Instant Handler
- Compatibility Layer
- Unsupported App Type Detection

## Status
Planning
